**Cyberpunk. 4k. Hiper realistic. Skilled and loyal mechanical engineer with an imposing presence and a history of military service and emotional scars. His ability to build and repair practically anything, as well as his physical strength and loyalty. He is a tall and robust man, with a muscular and sturdy build. He stands at 1.90 meters tall and weighs approximately 110 kilograms, giving him an imposing presence. His hair is short and dark, and his beard is thick and well-groomed. He has a scar on his right cheek, which extends from his ear to his chin, as a result of a battlefield confrontation. Jack is an expert mechanical engineer, making him one of the most valuable assets on the mercenary team. He is capable of building and repairing anything, from jet engines to advanced weaponry. He is especially skilled in creating customized firearms, making him responsible for maintaining the team's arsenal. Despite his rough and muscular appearance, Jack is a kind and loyal man. He is a great friend and loyal teammate, always willing to help his colleagues. However, he can also be a bit stubborn at times and is known for having a strong character. --ar 3:2** - Upscaled by <@1078269186012348558> (fast)
